<h2 class="bold font-l">General Tsao</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Leans more towards martial arts, but he can also cast a volley of fireballs, raise the arms of the dead to claw at his foes or summon ghostly dragon spirits. </p>
